Logical Model: AD: PostalAddress (V3 Data Type)

Official URL: http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/StructureDefinition/AD Version: 2.0.0-sd-202312-matchbox-patch
Active as of 2024-03-12 Computable Name: AD

Mailing and home or office addresses. A sequence of address parts, such as street or post office Box, city, postal code, country, etc.

Usage:

  • Use this Logical Model Profile: AssignedAuthor (CDA Class), AssignedEntity (CDA Class), AssociatedEntity (CDA Class), Criterion (CDA Class)...
